ship between the manager and the staff, which can, in turn, improve morale and efficiency.</li><li class=\"\">For effective targeted stakeholder communication, it is vital to know who the stakeholders are and what are their goals, motives and attitudes.</li><li class=\"\">The influencing factors of stakeholder communication are – the importance of stakeholders, the type of communication, the means of communication, its frequency and the time of communication.</li><li class=\"\">A communication strategy is a high-level view of communication objectives for any business, which are tied directly to the business and expected business benefits. A good communication plan includes who, what, where, when, and how.</li></ul></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li></ul>\n"]}